## 质量门禁 (Quality Gates)

### GATE-1: 数据获取验证
```python
# 验证数据存在且有效
assert profile is not None
assert profile.stock.code is not None
```

### GATE-2: 财务指标验证
```python
# 验证指标在合理范围
assert 0 <= metrics.roe <= 100  # ROE 应该在 0-100%
assert metrics.debt_to_asset <= 100
```

### GATE-3: 分析结果验证
```python
# 验证输出格式
assert isinstance(report, str)
assert len(report) > 100  # 报告不应为空
```

